msgctxt "YukariConnectPage"
msgid "About YukariConnect"
msgstr "关于 YukariConnect"

msgctxt "YukariConnectPage"
msgid "<html><head/><body><p>YukariConnect is a P2P networking solution (MPL-2.0 licensed) developed specifically for Luna Launcher that allows Minecraft players to connect without port forwarding or central servers.</p><p>The YukariConnect program needs to be downloaded and running to use P2P multiplayer features.</p></body></html>"
msgstr "<html><head/><body><p>YukariConnect 是专为 Luna Launcher 开发的 P2P 联机解决方案（采用 MPL-2.0 许可证），允许 Minecraft 玩家无需端口映射或中心服务器即可连接。</p><p>需要下载并运行 YukariConnect 程序才能使用 P2P 多人游戏功能。</p></body></html>"

