msgctxt "TerracottaPage"
msgid "<html><head/><body><p>Terracotta is a P2P networking solution that allows Minecraft players to connect without port forwarding or central servers. It uses EasyTier to create direct connections between players.</p><p>The Terracotta program needs to be downloaded and running to use P2P multiplayer features.</p></body></html>"
msgstr "<html><head/><body><p>Terracotta 是一款 P2P 联机解决方案，允许 Minecraft 玩家无需端口映射或中心服务器即可连接。它使用 EasyTier 在玩家之间建立直接连接。</p><p>需要下载并运行 Terracotta 程序才能使用 P2P 多人游戏功能。</p></body></html>"

