msgctxt "AuthlibInjectorPage"
msgid "<html><head/><body><p>authlib-injector is a Java agent that allows Minecraft to use custom Yggdrasil authentication servers (such as LittleSkin or custom skin servers).</p><p>It is automatically downloaded when you launch a game with a Yggdrasil account, but you can also manage it here.</p><p>For more information, visit <a href=\"https://authlib-injector.yushi.moe/\">authlib-injector.yushi.moe</a></p></body></html>"
msgstr "<html><head/><body><p>authlib-injector 是一款 Java 代理，允许 Minecraft 使用自定义 Yggdrasil 认证服务器（如 LittleSkin 或自定义皮肤服务器）。</p><p>使用 Yggdrasil 账号启动游戏时会自动下载，但您也可以在此处管理它。</p><p>更多信息请访问 <a href=\"https://authlib-injector.yushi.moe/\">authlib-injector.yushi.moe</a></p></body></html>"

